{"tid":394010,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得 網絡拯救咗好多人嘅生命？","createTime":"2017-09-09T15:09:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-09T16:30:44.000Z","uid":35370,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"04a9daa5031966ec5d08e71290b5a578c02ce21e","tid":394010,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T15:09:15.000Z","msg":"寂寞嘅人可以搵到交談嘅對象<br />\n冇人識嘅網絡作家，藝術家，gamer等等搵到平台分享<br />\n覺得世界好沉悶嘅人，網絡有好多嘢比佢擴闊眼界<br />\n<br />\n如果冇咗網絡，而我哋活係其他嘢相同嘅世界，可能我哋當中好多人一早就捱唔住自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利伸： 一個人長大，細個嘅時候靠上論壇解悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果冇網絡，成個童年都變得難以想像"},{"pid":"d6770d63d64888a9bc6a94578a62f5b4ccee6db5","tid":394010,"uid":6869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T15:15:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c9a739fd62daeec22c55c92d6b53a4565ee6ebce","tid":394010,"uid":137766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T15:16:55.000Z","msg":"有利有弊"},{"pid":"753b52d0256cb5b951251e30fa2c21bf6817450f","tid":394010,"uid":145008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T15:19:21.000Z","msg":"無網絡無得睇青如bb個mk妹故"},{"pid":"ee5008e269011b60612ac9a571f64d0876ae58d7","tid":394010,"uid":129494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T15:24:40.000Z","msg":"手殘撳錯負皮sor <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"279040bbc5033ce08afd2349ff36f80cc96e46e3","tid":394010,"uid":139272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T15:32:56.000Z","msg":"咁又係啊，起碼無野做都可以上forum解悶<br />\n睇下Post又一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceb2047fffeae6259f34eb987de7e4346cc1b77f","tid":394010,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T15:45:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁又係啊，起碼無野做都可以上forum解悶<br />\n睇下Post又一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"